---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import AffiliateButton from '../../components/AffiliateButton.astro';

const title = "Mind Lab Pro versus Hunter Focus: The Ultimate Brain Booster Showdown 2026";
const description = "A clinical comparison between Mind Lab Pro and Hunter Focus. We analyze the dosages and ingredient synergy to find the best nootropic for your cognitive demands.";
---

<MainLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <article>
      <!-- Article Header -->
      <header class="mb-12 text-center">
        <span class="text-xs uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 mb-4 block font-semibold">Nootropics Comparison</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl text-slate-900 leading-tight mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">
          Mind Lab Pro versus Hunter Focus: The Ultimate Brain Booster Showdown 2026
        </h1>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-3 mt-8">
          <span class="bg-slate-50 text-slate-900 border border-slate-200 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full">Editorial Review</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-slate-500">Updated May 2026</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="w-full h-64 md:h-96 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-12 shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
        <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/3683074/pexels-photo-3683074.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1200" alt="Mind Lab Pro vs Hunter Focus" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      </div>

      <!-- Article Content -->
      <div class="prose prose-slate prose-lg max-w-none text-slate-700">
        <p class="lead text-xl italic text-slate-900 mb-8" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">
          In an era of constant digital distraction, cognitive enhancers, or nootropics, have moved from Silicon Valley offices to the mainstream. Today, we compare two of the most respected names in the industry: Mind Lab Pro, the universal nootropic, and Hunter Focus, the high potency specialist.
        </p>

        <p class="mb-10">
          At Wellness Sanctuary, we have analyzed the clinical dosages and ingredient synergy to see which formula actually delivers on the promise of limitless focus.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-3xl text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">1. The Strategy Behind the Formulas</h2>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-xl mb-8 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Mind Lab Pro</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-0">
            Known as a clean nootropic. It uses 11 evidence-based ingredients designed to optimize 6 different brain pathways. It is completely caffeine free, making it ideal for those who want steady focus without the jitters.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-slate-50 p-8 rounded-xl mb-12 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Hunter Focus</h3>
          <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed mb-0">
            This is a more aggressive, high dose formula. It includes 20 ingredients, featuring a larger serving size and a more diverse range of adaptogens and vitamins to combat mental fatigue under high pressure environments.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">2. Comparison Table</h2>
        
        <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-12">
          <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-b-2 border-slate-900">
                <th class="py-4 px-4 text-slate-900 font-bold">Feature</th>
                <th class="py-4 px-4 text-slate-900 font-bold">Mind Lab Pro</th>
                <th class="py-4 px-4 text-slate-900 font-bold">Hunter Focus</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Active Ingredients</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">11 Clean Label</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">20 High Potency</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Caffeine Content</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">0mg Stimulant Free</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">0mg Stimulant Free</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Key Strength</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Long Term Brain Health</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">Immediate Mental Clarity</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-slate-50">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Serving Size</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">2 Capsules</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4">6 Capsules</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-b border-slate-200">
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-semibold text-slate-500">Best For</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-bold text-slate-900">Daily Consistency</td>
                <td class="py-4 px-4 font-bold text-slate-900">High Stakes Productivity</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl text-slate-900 mt-12 mb-6" style="font-family:'Noto Serif',serif;">3. Our Editorial Verdict</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 mb-10">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-slate-900 pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Choose Mind Lab Pro if</p>
            <p class="text-sm">You are looking for a highly efficient, sustainable supplement that supports memory and brain regeneration without a heavy daily pill count.</p>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <AffiliateButton id="mind-lab-pro" text="Try Mind Lab Pro" />
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="border-l-4 border-emerald-600 pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Choose Hunter Focus if</p>
            <p class="text-sm">You are a professional or student facing intense mental workloads and need the most comprehensive list of cognitive ingredients available on the market today.</p>
            <div class="mt-4">
              <AffiliateButton id="hunter-focus" text="Try Hunter Focus" />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <hr class="border-slate-200 my-12" />

        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center border border-slate-200">
          <span class="text-3xl mb-4 block">🧠</span>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Scientific Insight</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-8">
            Both products avoid proprietary blends, meaning they disclose the exact dosage of every ingredient. This is a standard of transparency we highly value at Wellness Sanctuary.
          </p>
          
          <h4 class="text-lg font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Not sure which one fits your lifestyle</h4>
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-700 mb-6">
            Take our Interactive Focus Quiz to determine which cognitive profile matches your current mental demands.
          </p>
          <a href="/quiz" class="inline-block bg-emerald-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-xl text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-emerald-700 transition-all shadow-md">
            Find My Program
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</MainLayout>
